column5: It's beginning to look a lot like fishing all around the bay it is freezing up I just might be icefishing next week link to photos

TY brother Terry.  I will be out looking at the new and improved ice fishing gadgets. Gave all my stuff to the oldest boy   . Good reason to say,dear,I need it,really I do.You did say get out of the house after all.
Couch is looking very nice...might just be a road trip Saturday or Sunday  Thx for posting that pic Terry

Be careful of anything with snow on it.. I thought with me leaving the submersible pump on the pool cover that it was stuck there 'till spring with these cold temps. Thought today.. I'll climb on there and chip it out from below a few inches of ice...... the first step wasn't very dry!!!!!!!!
